<h2 id="title">Dialogs</h2>

<p>{{#mdc-button style="unelevated" click=(action (mut showBasicDialog) "basic")}}Show Basic Dialog{{/mdc-button}}</p>
<p>{{#mdc-button style="unelevated" click=(action (mut showScrollableDialog) "scrollable")}}Show Scrollable Dialog{{/mdc-button}}</p>
<p>{{#mdc-button style="unelevated" click=(action (mut showDefaultDialog) "default")}}Show Default Dialog{{/mdc-button}}</p>

{{#mdc-dialog title="Use Google's location service?"
              accept=(action "accept")
              acceptButtonText="Accept"
              close=(action "close")
              closeButtonText="Decline"
              show=showBasicDialog}}
  Let Google help apps determine location. This means sending anonymous
  location data to Google, even when no apps are running.
{{/mdc-dialog}}

